'''Crandor Ijjix''' was a [[Norat]] hostage taken by the [[Yevetha]] during the attack. Along with the other hostages taken during the [[Yevethan Purge]], Crandor was forced to record a message begging the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] not to fire on Yevethan ships carrying prisoners. The Yevetha played the messages during the [[Battle of Doornik-319|Blockade of Doornik-319]], causing hesitation from the New Republic ships and forcing them to withdraw.

